Then for the restricted MLE is 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(\theta_{0},n^{-1}\sum_{i=1}^{n}\left(X_{i}-\theta_{0}\right)^{2}\right)$
\end_inset

 if 
\begin_inset Formula $\theta_{0}\leq\bar{x}$
\end_inset

